SELECT DISTINCT 5
    o.orderno
    ,NTH_VALUE(ol.itemno, 1) OVER top_five_items AS item1
    ,NTH_VALUE(ol.itemno, 2) OVER top_five_items AS item2
    ,NTH_VALUE(ol.itemno, 3) OVER top_five_items AS item3
    ,NTH_VALUE(ol.itemno, 4) OVER top_five_items AS item4
    ,NTH_VALUE(ol.itemno, 5) OVER top_five_items AS item5
FROM
    order AS o
    JOIN order_line AS ol USING (orderno)
WINDOW
    top_five_items AS (PARTITION BY ol.orderno ORDER BY ol.itemno)
